  ## ü§ù Contributing
  
  Contributions are welcome! Feel free to:
  - Add new endpoints
  - Improve existing tests
  - Fix bugs or issues
  - Enhance documentation
  
  ## üìù Notes
  
  - All requests use the public GitHub API (no authentication required by default)
  - Rate limits apply: 60 requests/hour (unauthenticated), 5000/hour (authenticated)
  - Response times may vary based on GitHub's API performance
  - Some tests validate specific repositories (usebruno/bruno, usebruno/bruno-website)
  
